{"type": "root", "attrs": {"type": "node", "context": "sop", "namespace": "kinefx", "internal": "motionclipcycle", "icon": "SOP/kinefx-motionclipcycle", "tags": "animation", "version": "2.0", "since": "19.0"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["MotionClip Cycle"], "extent": [151, 172]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Smoothly loops a section of a MotionClip"], "extent": [172, 221]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This SOP takes as input a MotionClip (eg. from ", {"scheme": null, "value": "kinefx--motionclip", "type": "link", "text": ["MotionClip"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/kinefx--motionclip.html"}, ")\nand a frame range. It outputs a clip containing the specified number of repetitions,\nblending between each of them."], "extent": [221, 418]}, {"level": 1, "id": "state", "container": true, "type": "state_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [418, 425], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This viewport state allows you to visualize a MotionClip or its evaluated poses over time using a color ramp, and it is available for every MotionClip SOP node that outputs a MotionClip."], "extent": [425, 614]}, {"level": 3, "type": "sep", "indent": 0, "text": [" MotionClip viewport state interaction "], "extent": [614, 660], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["You can select individual joints from the current pose in the MotionClip viewport state. For the selected joints, you can then use the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Evaluate Pose"]}, " mode to view just the current pose, its selected joints, and the motion trails for those joints."], "extent": [9948, 10203]}, {"type": "video_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "video", "indent": 4, "role": "item", "extent": [10203, 10215], "body": [{"type": "summary", "indent": 8, "text": ["rFoot and lFoot joints selected, Mode = Evaluate Pose, Color = White to Red"], "extent": [10302, 10393]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"src": "/videos/kinefx_moclipviewstate_jointmotiontrail.mp4", "loop": "false"}}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true}, {"level": 3, "type": "sep", "indent": 0, "text": [" MotionClip viewport state toolbar "], "extent": [726, 768], "body": [{"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 4, "text": ["Mode"], "extent": [10463, 10473], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Determines the MotionClip information that is displayed in the viewport."], "extent": [10499, 10581]}, {"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["MotionClip"], "extent": [10581, 10601], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Displays all the MotionClip\u2019s poses."], "extent": [10601, 10651]}, {"type": "fig_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "fig", "indent": 12, "text": [" ", {"scheme": "Image", "value": "/images/nodes/sop/kinefx_moclipviewstate_mode01.jpg", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "role": "item", "extent": [10651, 10729], "body": [{"type": "summary", "indent": 16, "text": ["Mode = MotionClip"], "extent": [10765, 10806]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"display": "left full"}}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["Evaluate Pose"], "extent": [10806, 10829], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Displays a single MotionClip pose at the current time."], "extent": [10829, 10897]}, {"type": "fig_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "fig", "indent": 12, "text": [" ", {"scheme": "Image", "value": "/images/nodes/sop/kinefx_moclipviewstate_mode02.jpg", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "role": "item", "extent": [10897, 10975], "body": [{"type": "summary", "indent": 16, "text": ["Mode = Evaluate Pose"], "extent": [11011, 11055]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"display": "left full"}}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "moclip_mode"}}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 4, "text": ["Transparent MotionClip"], "extent": [11055, 11083], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["When turned on, the MotionClip\u2019s poses are displayed as fainter lines, making it easier to see the scene behind the MotionClip, as well as the evaluated pose."], "extent": [11083, 11251]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 4, "text": ["Color"], "extent": [11251, 11262], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Applies the selected color ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/network/ramps", "type": "link", "text": ["ramp"], "fullpath": "/network/ramps.html"}, " preset to the MotionClip\u2019s visualization in the viewport. This color ramp helps to visualize changes to the MotionClip or individual poses over time."], "extent": [11289, 11497]}, {"type": "video_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "video", "indent": 8, "role": "item", "extent": [11497, 11513], "body": [{"type": "summary", "indent": 12, "text": ["Mode = Evaluate Pose, Color = White to Red"], "extent": [11609, 11671]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"src": "/videos/kinefx_moclipviewstate_evaluateposecolor.mp4", "loop": "false"}}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "moclip_color"}}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 4, "text": ["Extend Color"], "extent": [11671, 11689], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Determines how the poses outside of the MotionClip\u2019s defined animation start and end range are visualized in the viewport."], "extent": [11722, 11854]}, {"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["Hold"], "extent": [11854, 11868], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Holds the color values at the ends of the range."], "extent": [11868, 11930]}, {"type": "fig_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "fig", "indent": 12, "text": [" ", {"scheme": "Image", "value": "/images/nodes/sop/kinefx_moclipviewstate_extendcolorhold.jpg", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "role": "item", "extent": [11930, 12017], "body": [{"type": "summary", "indent": 16, "text": ["Mode = MotionClip, Color = Plasma, Extended Color = Hold"], "extent": [12053, 12133]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"display": "left full"}}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["Gray"], "extent": [12133, 12147], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Poses outside the animation start and end range are colored gray."], "extent": [12147, 12226]}, {"type": "fig_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "fig", "indent": 12, "text": [" ", {"scheme": "Image", "value": "/images/nodes/sop/kinefx_moclipviewstate_extendcolorgray.jpg", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "role": "item", "extent": [12226, 12313], "body": [{"type": "summary", "indent": 16, "text": ["Mode = MotionClip, Color = Plasma, Extended Color = Gray"], "extent": [12349, 12429]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"display": "left full"}}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["Hide"], "extent": [12429, 12443], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Hides the poses outside the animation start and end range."], "extent": [12443, 12515]}, {"type": "fig_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "fig", "indent": 12, "text": [" ", {"scheme": "Image", "value": "/images/nodes/sop/kinefx_moclipviewstate_extendcolorhide.jpg", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "role": "item", "extent": [12515, 12602], "body": [{"type": "summary", "indent": 16, "text": ["Mode = MotionClip, Color = Plasma, Extended Color = Hide"], "extent": [12638, 12717]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"display": "left full"}}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "moclip_extendcolor"}}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "text": "State"}, {"level": 1, "id": "parameters", "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [828, 840], "body": [{"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Cycle"], "extent": [840, 853], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Frame Range"], "extent": [853, 871], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Specifies the start/end/increment of the range of frames to be cycled."], "extent": [891, 971]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "range"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Cycles Before"], "extent": [971, 990], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The number of cycles to output before the specified range."], "extent": [1025, 1093]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["This does not need to be an integer, it can output a fraction of a cycle."], "extent": [1093, 1176]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "cyclesbefore"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Cycles After"], "extent": [1176, 1194], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The number of cycles to output after the specified range."], "extent": [1228, 1295]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "cyclesafter"}, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"level": 3, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 4, "text": ["Locomotion"], "extent": [1295, 1318], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["These parameters manage how the locomotion of the MotionClip will be computed and cycled."], "extent": [1318, 1422]}, {"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 8, "text": ["Sequence Cycles"], "extent": [1422, 1447], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["The method used to sequence the cycles."], "extent": [1478, 1531]}, {"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 12, "text": ["By Shifting Between Cycles"], "extent": [1531, 1571], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 16, "text": ["Each cycle will begin where the previous cycle ended."], "extent": [1571, 1642]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 12, "text": ["By Blending Velocity"], "extent": [1642, 1676], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 16, "text": ["The velocity of each frame of the input MotionClip will be blended and used to sequence each frame of the output MotionClip."], "extent": [1676, 1818]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 12, "text": ["Mirror Odd Cycles"], "extent": [1818, 1849], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 16, "text": ["Every other cycle will be reversed."], "extent": [1849, 1902]}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "sequencetype"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 8, "text": ["Locomotion"], "extent": [1902, 1922], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["The method used to determine the locomotion of the MotionClip and cycle it."], "extent": [1963, 2052]}, {"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 12, "text": ["None"], "extent": [2052, 2070], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 16, "text": ["The locomotion will not be computed and the MotionClip will be cycled without translating or rotating it between cycles."], "extent": [2070, 2220]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 12, "text": ["Existing Locomotion"], "extent": [2220, 2253], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 16, "text": ["The locomotion will be obtained from the ", {"type": "code", "text": ["__locomotion__"]}, " point of the MotionClip. This point should be created by the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "kinefx--extractlocomotion", "type": "link", "text": ["Extract Locomotion"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/kinefx--extractlocomotion.html"}, " node."], "extent": [2253, 2442]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 12, "text": ["Compute Locomotion"], "extent": [2442, 2474], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 16, "text": ["The locomotion of the MotionClip will be computed by this node."], "extent": [2474, 2555]}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "locomotion"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 8, "text": ["Locomotion Source"], "extent": [2555, 2582], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["The source of the locomotion of the MotionClip."], "extent": [2616, 2677]}, {"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 12, "text": ["Joint"], "extent": [2677, 2696], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 16, "text": ["A joint in the skeletons of the MotionClip will be used as a reference for extracting the locomotion."], "extent": [2696, 2815]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 12, "text": ["Center of Mass"], "extent": [2815, 2843], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 16, "text": ["The center of mass of the skeletons of the MotionClip will be computed and used as a reference for extracting the locomotion."], "extent": [2843, 2986]}], "container": true}], "container": true}, {"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["This parameter is only available when ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Locomotion"]}, " is set to ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Compute Locomotion"]}, "."], "extent": [2986, 3086]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "locomotionsource"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 8, "text": ["Locomotion Joint"], "extent": [3086, 3112], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["The name of the joint in the input MotionClip which will be used to compute the locomotion and to translate and rotate the clip between cycles."], "extent": [3146, 3303]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["This parameter is only available when ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Locomotion Source"]}, " is set to ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Joint"]}, "."], "extent": [3303, 3397]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "locomotionjoint"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 8, "text": ["COM Joint"], "extent": [3397, 3416], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Name of the COM joint in the input skeleton to use as reference for extracting the translation and orientation."], "extent": [3447, 3572]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["This parameter is only available when ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Locomotion Source"]}, " is set to ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Center of Mass"]}, "."], "extent": [3572, 3675]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "comtargetname"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 8, "text": ["Configuration Attribute"], "extent": [3675, 3708], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["The name of the configuration point attribute from which to read the ", {"type": "code", "text": ["mass"]}, " and ", {"type": "code", "text": ["local_com"]}, " attributes from.\n            See ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/kinefx__configurejoints", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/kinefx__configurejoints.html"}, "."], "extent": [3745, 3919]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["This parameter is only available when ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Locomotion Source"]}, " is set to ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Center of Mass"]}, "."], "extent": [3919, 4022]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "configurationattrib"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 8, "text": ["Shift Cycles"], "extent": [4022, 4044], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["The number of frames by which to shift the subsequent cycles. "], "extent": [4074, 4162]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["If the value is ", {"type": "code", "text": ["0"]}, ", each cycle will start at the same position and orientation that the previous cycle ended."], "extent": [4162, 4298]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["If the value is negative ", {"type": "code", "text": ["n"]}, ", each cycle will be shifted so that it starts at the same position and orientation as the skeleton was ", {"type": "code", "text": ["n"]}, " frames before the last frame of the previous cycle."], "extent": [4298, 4511]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["If the value is positive ", {"type": "code", "text": ["n"]}, ", each cycle will be shifted so that it starts at the same position and orientation the skeleton would have been ", {"type": "code", "text": ["n"]}, " frames after the beginning of this cycle, had it not been shifted."], "extent": [4511, 4736]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["This parameter is only available when ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Sequence Cycles"]}, " is set to ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["By Shifting Between Cycles"]}, "."], "extent": [4736, 4849]}, {"type": "tip_group", "body": [{"type": "tip", "indent": 12, "role": "item", "extent": [4849, 4866], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 16, "text": ["If you want the cycles to continue moving forward between cycles, try setting this to ", {"type": "code", "text": ["1"]}, "."], "extent": [4866, 4974]}], "container": true}, {"type": "tip", "indent": 12, "role": "item", "extent": [4974, 4991], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 16, "text": ["When using the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Overlap Sequences"]}, " blend method, try setting the value of this to ", {"type": "code", "text": ["'1 - ch(\"region\")'"]}, " so that the first frames involved in the blend overlap."], "extent": [4991, 5181]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "shiftcycles"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 8, "text": ["Apply Locomotion"], "extent": [5181, 5207], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["The animation will be shifted by its locomotion."], "extent": [5253, 5315]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["This parameter is only available when ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Locomotion"]}, " is set to ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Existing Locomotion"]}, "."], "extent": [5315, 5416]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "applylocomotion"}, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"level": 4, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 8, "text": ["Translation"], "extent": [5416, 5444], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["These parameters manage how the position of the locomotion of the MotionClip will be computed and cycled."], "extent": [5444, 5564]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["When ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Sequence Cycles"]}, " is set to ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["By Blending Velocity"]}, ", only ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Shift Axes"]}, " is available."], "extent": [5564, 5672]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["These parameters are only available when ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Locomotion"]}, " is set to ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Compute Locomotion"]}, "."], "extent": [5672, 5783]}, {"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 12, "text": ["Match Translation"], "extent": [5783, 5814], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 16, "text": ["The method of choosing the joint which will begin at the translation where the previous iteration left off."], "extent": [5869, 6010]}, {"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 16, "text": ["None"], "extent": [6010, 6032], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 20, "text": ["Do not match translations."], "extent": [6032, 6080]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 16, "text": ["Locomotion Joint"], "extent": [6080, 6114], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 20, "text": ["The joint provided in the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Locomotion Joint"]}, " parameter will be chosen."], "extent": [6114, 6224]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 16, "text": ["Custom Joint"], "extent": [6224, 6254], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 20, "text": ["The joint provided in the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Translation Joint"]}, " parameter will be chosen."], "extent": [6254, 6349]}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "matchtranslation"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 12, "text": ["Translation Joint"], "extent": [6349, 6380], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 16, "text": ["This joint will begin at the translation where the previous iteration left off."], "extent": [6428, 6525]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "relativejointtranslations"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 12, "text": ["Shift Axes"], "extent": [6525, 6549], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 16, "text": ["Choose on which axes to shift the cycles."], "extent": [6581, 6640]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "shiftaxes"}, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}, {"level": 4, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 8, "text": ["Orientation"], "extent": [6640, 6668], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["These parameter manage how the orientation of the locomotion of the MotionClip will be computed and cycled."], "extent": [6668, 6802]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["These parameters are only available when ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Locomotion"]}, " is set to ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Compute Locomotion"]}, "."], "extent": [6802, 6905]}, {"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 12, "text": ["Method"], "extent": [6905, 6925], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 16, "text": ["Specify around which axes to match the orientation. See below for details on the parameters for each of these options."], "extent": [6965, 7101]}, {"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 16, "text": ["None"], "extent": [7101, 7123], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 20, "text": ["Do not match orientations."], "extent": [7123, 7171]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 16, "text": ["Around Up Axis"], "extent": [7171, 7203], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 20, "text": ["Match the orientation around the Up axis of the character. The Up axis will be deduced from the viewport orientation option."], "extent": [7203, 7349]}, {"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 20, "text": ["Up Axis"], "extent": [7349, 7378], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 24, "text": ["Specify which method to use when extracting the orientation around the Up axis. See below for details on the parameters for each of these options."], "extent": [7378, 7550]}, {"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 24, "text": ["Use Joint Orientation"], "extent": [7550, 7597], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 28, "text": ["Extract the orientation by pulling out the Euler angles from the locomotion joint and uses those to extract orientation data around the chosen axis."], "extent": [7597, 7775]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 24, "text": ["Direction Between Joints"], "extent": [7775, 7825], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 28, "text": ["Extract the orientation by specifying an extra joint and drawing a direction vector between the locomotion joint and the joint specified in ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Look At Joint"]}, ". This direction vector will be projected on the relevant plane and used to determine the orientation around the chosen axis."], "extent": [7825, 8137]}, {"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 28, "text": ["Look At Joint"], "extent": [8137, 8180], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 32, "text": ["Specify an extra joint that will act as the tip of the direction vector."], "extent": [8230, 8336]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "updirvector"}}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 16, "text": ["Around All Axes"], "extent": [8336, 8369], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 20, "text": ["Match the orientation around all axes of the character."], "extent": [8369, 8446]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 16, "text": ["Custom"], "extent": [8446, 8470], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 20, "text": ["Customize which axis and which method you want to use for extracting the orientation of the character."], "extent": [8470, 8594]}, {"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 20, "text": ["Rotation Order"], "extent": [8594, 8630], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 24, "text": ["Specify which rotation order to use when extracting the orientation from the character animation."], "extent": [8630, 8753]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 20, "text": ["X Axis"], "extent": [8753, 8781], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 24, "text": ["Specify which method to use when extracting the orientation around the X axis. See the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Up Axis"]}, " above for details on the parameters for each of these options."], "extent": [8829, 9016]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "xorientationmethod"}}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 20, "text": ["Y Axis"], "extent": [9016, 9044], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 24, "text": ["Specify which method to use when extracting the orientation around the Y axis. See the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Up Axis"]}, " above for details on the parameters for each of these options."], "extent": [9092, 9279]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "yorientationmethod"}}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 20, "text": ["Z Axis"], "extent": [9279, 9307], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 24, "text": ["Specify which method to use when extracting the orientation around the Z axis. See the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Up Axis"]}, " above for details on the parameters for each of these options."], "extent": [9355, 9542]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "zorientationmethod"}}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "orientationmethod"}, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}]}]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Attributes"], "extent": [9542, 9559], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["These parameters are used to determine which attributes from the input MotionClip become animated on the output MotionClip."], "extent": [9559, 9688]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["For more details on what distinguishes an animated attribute from a rest attribute, see the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Attributes"]}, " folder on the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "kinefx--motionclipevaluate", "type": "link", "text": ["MotionClip Evaluate SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/kinefx--motionclipevaluate.html"}, "."], "extent": [9688, 9868]}, {"type": "tip_group", "body": [{"type": "tip", "indent": 4, "role": "item", "extent": [9868, 9877], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["To maintain the attributes which were previously animated without adding any additional attributes to the poses, toggle ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Repack Attributes"]}, " on, clear ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Rest Attributes"]}, ", and set ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Animated Attributes"]}, " to ", {"type": "code", "text": ["*"]}, "."], "extent": [9877, 10099]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Theses are the default values for these parameters."], "extent": [10099, 10160]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Repack Attributes"], "extent": [10160, 10183], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["When enabled, the attributes defined by the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Rest Attributes"]}, " and ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Animated Attributes"]}, " patterns will be evaluated from the input MotionClip and packed into the output MotionClip\u2019s poses.\n            This will result in all of these attributes becoming animated attributes on the output MotionClip."], "extent": [10215, 10531]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "repackattribs"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Rest Attributes"], "extent": [10531, 10552], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The attributes that should be unpacked from the rest pose of the input MotionClip.\n        All attributes that match this pattern will become animated attributes on the output MotionClip."], "extent": [10578, 10775]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "restattribs"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Animated Attributes"], "extent": [10775, 10800], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The attributes that should be evaluated from the animated poses of the input MotionClip.\n        All attributes that match this pattern will remain animated on the output MotionClip."], "extent": [10826, 11018]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "animattribs"}, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Blend"], "extent": [11018, 11030], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Method"], "extent": [11030, 11043], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The method of blending."], "extent": [11072, 11105]}, {"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["Preserve Length"], "extent": [11105, 11130], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Keeps the total length of each cycle the same as the length of the input MotionClip. Blends the end of each cycle to be first frame of the next cycle."], "extent": [11130, 11302]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["Overlap Sequences"], "extent": [11302, 11329], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Overlaps the end of end cycle with the beginning of the previous cycle."], "extent": [11329, 11422]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 8, "text": ["Insert Blend Region"], "extent": [11422, 11451], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Inserts a region between the cycles where blending is done."], "extent": [11451, 11524]}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "method"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Blend Frames"], "extent": [11524, 11542], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The number of frames over which the blending is applied."], "extent": [11563, 11629]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "region"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Blend Start to End"], "extent": [11629, 11653], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["This enables blending from the end of the last cycle to the start of the first, allowing for seamless looping of the clip."], "extent": [11680, 11812]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "loop"}, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"level": 3, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 4, "text": ["Locomotion"], "extent": [11812, 11835], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["These parameters manage how the locomotion of the MotionClip should be blended.\n        The parameters that affect the blend of the locomotion will be obtained from the parameters that affect the blend of a joint in the MotionClip."], "extent": [11835, 12085]}, {"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 8, "text": ["Match Blend"], "extent": [12085, 12106], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["The method of choosing the joint from which the parameters and attributes that affect the blend of the locomotion will be obtained."], "extent": [12140, 12285]}, {"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 12, "text": ["None"], "extent": [12285, 12303], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 16, "text": ["No joint will be chosen and the locomotion will not be blended."], "extent": [12303, 12384]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 12, "text": ["Locomotion Joint"], "extent": [12384, 12427], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 16, "text": ["If ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Locomotion"]}, " is ", {"type": "ui", 